and his nonfiction book

00:00:27.850 --> 00:00:31.060
"The Transparent Society"
won the Freedom of Speech

00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:33.850
Award of the American
Library Association.

00:00:33.850 --> 00:00:36.270
His newest novel,
"Existence," explores

00:00:36.270 --> 00:00:39.880
the ultimate question--
billions of planets

00:00:39.880 --> 00:00:44.850
